## 🔹 Dry Run (nums = [1,1,2])

Sorted: [1,1,2]

Start:

→ pick 1 (index 0)  
→ pick 1 (index 1) → pick 2 → [1,1,2]  

→ backtrack  
→ pick 2 → pick 1 → [1,2,1]  

→ skip duplicate when needed  

→ pick 2 → pick 1 → pick 1 → [2,1,1]  

---

## 🔹 Key Concepts

- `visited[]` → track used elements  
- sorting → required for duplicate handling  
- duplicate condition → prevents same permutations  
- backtracking → choose → explore → unchoose  

---

